<section class="container" id="about">
  <div class="info_title info_vertical">
    <div class="row wow info_vertical animated fadeInDown">
      <div class="col-md-12 text-left">
        <p>
          Minishift is a tool that helps you run OKD locally by launching a single-node
          OKD cluster inside a virtual machine. With Minishift you can try out OKD or
          develop with it, day-to-day, on your local machine.
        </p>
        <p>
          You can run Minishift on the Windows, macOS, and GNU/Linux operating systems. Minishift
          uses <a href="https://github.com/docker/machine/tree/master/libmachine">libmachine</a>
          for provisioning virtual machines, and <a href="https://github.com/openshift/origin">OKD</a>
          for running the cluster.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

